&lt;p&gt;Review request for Flume.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Summary&lt;br/&gt;
-------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;TestAvroSink fails often for two reasons:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) We call close before the socket has started&lt;br/&gt;
2) We call sink.process before the socket has shutdown&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This puts a small sleep into fix those two issues.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This addresses bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-960&quot; title=&quot;TestAvroSink.testFailedConnect is racy and fails often&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLUME-960&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLUME-960&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-960&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-960&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Diffs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  flume-ng-core/src/test/java/org/apache/flume/sink/TestAvroSink.java a46acc0 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Diff: &lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.apache.org/r/3837/diff&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://reviews.apache.org/r/3837/diff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Testing&lt;br/&gt;
-------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After the change, I ran the test 120 times and it passed 120 times.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Thanks,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Brock&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
